В Линуксе можно переназначить горячие клавиши “Next Change” и “Previous Change”. По умолчанию Ctrl+Alt+Shift + Вниз/Вверх

Setup idea running jdk:
Search "Switch Boot JDK"
~/.IntelliJIdea2018.1/config/idea.jdk
with content: /usr/lib/jvm/java-8-oracle   (without quotes)
If file doesn't exist - default is bundled jdk in idea folder
Additional info: https://intellij-support.jetbrains.com/hc/en-us/articles/206544879-Selecting-the-JDK-version-the-IDE-will-run-under
